query getDocuments($limit: Int, $lastId: String, $from: String) {
    getDocuments(limit: $limit, lastId: $lastId, fromTimestamp: $from) {
        id
type
status
documentNumber
startDate
endDate
currencyCode
totalNetPrice
languageCode
updatedAt
resellerId
customerId
distributorId

vendorSpecificFields {
    vendor
    groupId
    groupDescription
    said
    ampId
    sar
}

contactPersons {
    phoneNumber
    name
    type
    mail
}

documentEntries {
    assetDocumentId
    assetId
    assetProductLine
    assetProductGroupDescription
    serviceGroupSku
    serviceGroupSkuDescription
    serviceLevelSku
    serviceLevelSkuDescription
    serviceFullDescription
    startDate
    endDate
    languageCode
    currencyCode
    listPrice
    estimatedValueRenewal
    assetProductType
    environmentId
    equipmentNumber
    lineItemListPrice
    lineItemMonthlyRetailPrice
    said
    sarNumber
    pspId
    pspName
    deletedAt
}
    }
}
